 ### tar, zip , unzip
-- tar
+#### tar
+
+Create tar Archive File in Linux
 ```
-# Create tar Archive File in Linux
 tar -cvf <tar-file>.tar <tar-dir>
-# Create gzip Archive File in Linux
+```
+Create gzip Archive File in Linux
+```
